IMAPAccount gmail
Host imap.gmail.com
User info@nvc.sg
PassCmd "security find-internet-password -w -a info@nvc.sg -s mbsync-gmail 2>/dev/null"
TLSType IMAPS
AuthMechs LOGIN

IMAPStore gmail-remote
Account gmail

MaildirStore gmail-local
Path ~/.mail/gmail/
Inbox ~/.mail/gmail/INBOX
SubFolders Verbatim

Channel gmail
Far :gmail-remote:
Near :gmail-local:
Patterns *
Create Both
Sync All
Expunge Both

# NVCSG Account (info@nvc.sg with dedicated Maildir)
IMAPAccount nvcsg
Host imap.gmail.com
User info@nvc.sg
PassCmd "security find-internet-password -w -a info@nvc.sg -s mbsync-gmail 2>/dev/null"
TLSType IMAPS
AuthMechs LOGIN

IMAPStore nvcsg-remote
Account nvcsg

MaildirStore nvcsg-local
Path ~/.mail/nvcsg/
Inbox ~/.mail/nvcsg/INBOX
SubFolders Verbatim

Channel nvcsg
Far :nvcsg-remote:
Near :nvcsg-local:
Patterns * ![Gmail]* "[Gmail]/Sent Mail" "[Gmail]/Drafts" "[Gmail]/All Mail"
Create Both
Sync All
Expunge Both
SyncState ~/.mail/nvcsg/.mbsync/
